---
const exclusions = [
  {
    number: '01',
    title: 'No envelope budgeting',
    description:
      "You won't allocate $47.50 to 'dining out' and feel guilty when you hit $48.",
  },
  {
    number: '02',
    title: 'No category budgets',
    description:
      "We auto-categorize your spending for awareness \u2014 but we'll never tell you that you've spent too much on coffee. If it's within your Safe to Spend, it's your call.",
  },
  {
    number: '03',
    title: 'No investment advice',
    description:
      "We're not trying to optimize your portfolio. We're trying to give you peace about daily spending.",
  },
  {
    number: '04',
    title: 'No cryptocurrency',
    description:
      'No NFTs. No meme coins. Just simple, clear money management.',
  },
];
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-36 bg-warm-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-storehouse-600 font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase reveal">
        What we leave out
      </p>
      <h2 class="mt-4 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-text-deep leading-[1.05] reveal reveal-delay-1">
        What Storehouse<br />doesn't do.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-muted leading-relaxed reveal reveal-delay-2">
        We believe in doing one thing well. Here's what we intentionally leave out:
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Exclusions as editorial numbered list -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-0 divide-y divide-text-faint/15">
      {exclusions.map((item) => (
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-8 py-10 md:py-12 reveal">
          <!-- X icon + number -->
          <div class="md:col-span-1 flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-faint flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
            </svg>
          </div>

          <!-- Title -->
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl text-text-deep leading-tight">
              {item.title}
            </h3>
          </div>

          <!-- Description -->
          <div class="md:col-span-8">
            <p class="text-lg text-text-body leading-relaxed">
              {item.description}
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Closing statement -->
    <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl bg-storehouse-50 border border-storehouse-200/60 p-8 sm:p-10 reveal">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="font-display text-xl sm:text-2xl text-text-deep leading-snug">
          Storehouse is not everything.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-text-body">
          It's the one thing that matters most: knowing what's safe to spend.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
